text: A friend of mine is looking for a new marketing company to re-design his company’s site and take over their social media account.  They are Premier Store Fixtures - a retail design firm that does env. design and for dicks, nike, underarmour.   Recs would be appreciated.
FINE does a lot of brand/marketing/digital work. I worked there for 5 years and they’re great people who do solid work.
